<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Borivali - Mumbai Suburban</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif; background: #f0f2f5; display: flex; justify-content: center; padding: 20px; }
        .mumbai-card { background: white; width: 480px; border-radius: 12px; box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); border-left: 10px solid #1a73e8; overflow: hidden; }
        .header { background: #f8f9fa; padding: 20px; text-align: center; }
        .content { padding: 25px; line-height: 1.6; }
        .highlight { color: #1a73e8; font-weight: bold; }
        .landmark { background: #e8f0fe; padding: 2px 6px; border-radius: 4px; font-size: 0.9em; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="mumbai-card">
        <div class="header"><h1>🚉 Borivali</h1><p>Mumbai Suburban District</p></div>
        <div class="content">
            <p><strong>Zone:</strong> North Mumbai</p>
            <p><strong>Primary Landmark:</strong> <span class="landmark">Sanjay Gandhi National Park</span></p>
            <p><strong>Major Attractions:</strong> Kanheri Caves, Global Vipassana Pagoda (Nearby)</p>
            <p><strong>Railway Code:</strong> <span class="highlight">BVI</span></p>
            <p><strong>Vibe:</strong> Lush greenery meets high-rise urban living.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
